---
# Tests live below this file. GoogleTest (`TEST(...)`) and rapidcheck
# (`RC_GTEST_PROP(...)`) macros expand to global-scope free functions
# the framework discovers through static initialisers; static / anon-
# namespace would defeat the discovery. Inherit the project-wide
# strict tidy and only loosen the linkage check inside test trees.
InheritParentConfig: true
Checks: >
  -misc-use-internal-linkage
...
